      "font_size_pt": 10.0
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Unless otherwise noted, our work will concentrate on the historical financial information of the last two fiscal years ended December 31, 2023 (“FY23”), December 31, 2024 (“FY24”) and the most recent available year-to-date financial information for 2025 (“YTD25”) for Hand Over Hand, LLC (“Target”).",
